casebody.data:
Miscellaneous Orders.

No. 360, Misc. No. 366, Misc. No. 385, Misc. No. 408, Misc. Wagner v. Louisiana; Haines v. Ragen, Warden; Pierce v. Cranor, Superintendent; and Taylor v. Squier, Warden.

The motions for leave to file petitions for writs of habeas corpus in these cases are severally denied.
